In a few words sometimes the connection between client and server doesn't go right, and errno is set on
EBUSY, other times the connection goes right, but send () fails, returns me -1 and errno is set on ENOTCONN.
I think the errors are given due to the same issue, but I haven't still solved it.
As temporary fix I send a 404 error to the browser when necessary, but I'll try to solve soon this 
problem.
